Titolo: Armand and the Foppish Hat

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Armand and the Foppish Hat is a freeware adventure game by American developer Jeff Hanson for Apple Macintosh and Microsoft Windows computers.  It is about a pompous swashbuckler named Armand Restant who must track down the thief who stole his hat.  The game is similar in style to the older Legend of Zelda games for the Nintendo Entertainment System (NES) and Super Nintendo Entertainment System (SNES).